verses.roman:
'ei ta' dvitīya sūta romaharaṣaṇa
baladeva dekhi' ye nā kaila pratyudgama'

synonyms: ei ta'-this; dvitīya—second; sūta romaharaṣaṇa—of the name Romaharṣaṇa-sūta; baladeva dekhi'-seeing Lord Balarāma; ye—who; nā—not; kaila—did; pratyudgama—stand up.
translation: "Here I find the second Romaharṣaṇa-sūta, who did not stand to show honor when he saw Lord Balarāma."
